item.title: Major Event Planning During Winter XGames with Kyle Nelson
item.description: Kyle Nelson, our disaster meteorologist and ski patroller, joins us this week in his role as Planning Section Chief with the Winter XGames Aspen Incident Management Team. He shares his experiences planning and helping with operations for medical and response management during the games this year. Feed: https://disasterpodcast.com/feed/podcast
